paragraphs.title: Population Summary
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select to_char(tran_date,'MM') as month
    ,min(tran_date) as start_date
    ,max(tran_date) as end_date
    ,count(txn_uid) as attempt_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then 1 else 0 end) as approve_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then fraud_ind else 0 end) as fraud_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then fraud_ind else 0 end)/sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then 1 else 0 end) as fraud_rate    
    
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' and micr = '044115443392795776' then 1 else 0 end) as fla_ue_approve_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' and micr = '044115443392795776' then fraud_ind else 0 end) as fla_ue_fraud_count    
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' and micr = '044115443392795776' then fraud_ind else 0 end)/sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' and micr = '044115443392795776' then 1 else 0 end) as fla_ue_fraud_rate
    
from walmart_txn_data_final
group by to_char(tran_date,'MM')
order by start_date;

%sql
select 'TRAIN' as DATA_SET
    ,to_char(count(*),'999G999G999') as txn_count
    ,to_char(sum(FRAUD_IND),'999G999G999') as fraud_count
    ,to_char(avg(FRAUD_IND)*100,'99D999')||'%' as fraud_rate
    
from train_wmt

union

select 'TEST' as DATA_SET
    ,to_char(count(*),'999G999G999') as txn_count
    ,to_char(sum(FRAUD_IND),'999G999G999') as fraud_count

%script
drop table WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL_EVAL;

create table WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL_EVAL as
select t.*
    ,s.probability as prob

from WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL t
    ,WMT_GV_NN_EVAL s
where t.txn_uid=s.txn_uid
    and s.prediction = 1;

paragraphs.text:
%sql
select to_number(to_char(tran_date,'WW')) as week
    
    ,min(tran_date) as week_start
    ,max(tran_date) as week_end
    ,avg(prob) as avg_prob_fraud_pred

    ,count(txn_uid) as attempt_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then FRAUD_IND else 0 end) as approve_fraud_count
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then FRAUD_IND else 0 end)/sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then 1 else 0 end) as approve_fraud_rate

    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then TRAN_AMOUNT else 0 end) as approve_dollars
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then CLM_CHECK_AMT-CLM_SALVAGE_AMT else 0 end) as net_loss_dollars
    ,sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then CLM_CHECK_AMT-CLM_SALVAGE_AMT else 0 end)/sum(case when auth_ind = 'A' then TRAN_AMOUNT else 0 end) as NLR

    ,sum(case when MICR = '044115443392795776' then 1 else 0 end) as FLA_UE_CHECK_COUNT
    ,sum(case when MICR = '044115443392795776' and FRAUD_IND = 1 then 1 else 0 end) as FLA_UE_FRAUD_COUNT
    ,to_char(sum(case when MICR = '044115443392795776' and auth_ind = 'A' and FRAUD_IND = 1 then 1 else 0 end)/nullif(sum(case when MICR = '044115443392795776' and auth_ind = 'A' then 1 else 0 end),0),'9D999') as FLA_UE_APPROVED_FRAUD_RATE
    
from WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL_EVAL
where prob >= 0.012
group by to_number(to_char(tran_date,'WW'))
order by to_number(to_char(tran_date,'WW'));

%script
drop table train_wmt;
drop table test_wmt;

create table train_wmt as
select t.*
    ,abs(to_number(d.prob) - 50) as decile
    
from WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL_EVAL t
    ,BIN_TBL_TRAIN_VW d
where t.txn_uid=d.txn_uid;

create table test_wmt as
select t.*
    ,abs(to_number(d.prob) - 50) as decile
    
from WALMART_TXN_DATA_FINAL_EVAL t
    ,BIN_TBL_TEST_VW d
where t.txn_uid=d.txn_uid;

%script
drop table train_roll_up;
drop table test_roll_up;

create table train_roll_up as
select decile
    ,count(txn_uid) as tran_count
    ,sum(fraud_ind) as fraud_count
    ,sum(tran_amount) as approve_dollars
    ,(sum(CLM_CHECK_AMT) - sum(CLM_SALVAGE_AMT)) as net_loss_dollars
from train_wmt
group by decile
order by decile;

create table test_roll_up as
select decile
    ,count(txn_uid) as tran_count
    ,sum(fraud_ind) as fraud_count
    ,sum(tran_amount) as approve_dollars
    ,(sum(CLM_CHECK_AMT) - sum(CLM_SALVAGE_AMT)) as net_loss_dollars
from test_wmt
group by decile
order by decile;

%script
drop table train_perf;

create table train_perf
    (decile number(22)
    ,cum_percent_good_train   number(*,5)
    ,cum_percent_fraud_train   number(*,5)
    ,cum_percent_good_dlrs_train   number(*,5)
    ,cum_percent_fraud_dlrs_train   number(*,5)
    ,cum_fraud_dlrs_train   number(*,2)
    );

declare 
    v_total_good number;
    v_total_fraud number;
    v_total_good_dlrs number;
    v_total_fraud_dlrs number;
    
begin
    select sum(tran_count-fraud_count)
        ,sum(fraud_count)
        ,sum(approve_dollars - net_loss_dollars)
        ,sum(net_loss_dollars)
        into v_total_good
            ,v_total_fraud
            ,v_total_good_dlrs
            ,v_total_fraud_dlrs
    
    from train_roll_up;
    
insert into train_perf
    (decile
    ,cum_percent_good_train
    ,cum_percent_fraud_train
    ,cum_percent_good_dlrs_train
    ,cum_percent_fraud_dlrs_train
    ,cum_fraud_dlrs_train
    )
select decile
    ,sum((tran_count-fraud_count)/v_total_good) over (order by decile) as cum_percent_good
    ,sum(fraud_count/v_total_fraud) over (order by decile) as cum_percent_fraud
    ,sum((approve_dollars-net_loss_dollars)/v_total_good_dlrs) over (order by decile) as cum_percent_good_dlrs
    ,sum(net_loss_dollars/v_total_fraud_dlrs) over (order by decile) as cum_percent_fraud_dlrs
    ,sum(net_loss_dollars) over (order by decile)  as cum_net_losses

from train_roll_up;

commit;

EXCEPTION
WHEN others
THEN
    RAISE;
END;

%script
drop table compare_models;

create table compare_models as
select n.decile

    ,r.cum_percent_good_train
    ,r.cum_percent_fraud_train
    ,r.cum_percent_good_dlrs_train
    ,r.cum_percent_fraud_dlrs_train
    ,r.cum_fraud_dlrs_train
    ,r.cum_percent_fraud_train - r.cum_percent_good_train as ks_train

    ,n.cum_percent_good_test
    ,n.cum_percent_fraud_test
    ,n.cum_percent_good_dlrs_test
    ,n.cum_percent_fraud_dlrs_test
    ,n.cum_fraud_dlrs_test
    ,n.cum_percent_fraud_test - n.cum_percent_good_test as ks_test
    
from train_perf r
    ,test_perf n
where r.decile=n.decile(+)
order by n.decile;
